      "review_summary": "The PR adds `schtasks /Change /DISABLE` in `stopScheduledTask()` and `schtasks /Change /ENABLE` in `restartScheduledTask()` for Windows Scheduled Task lifecycle control.\n\nPR surface: Source +4. Total +4 across 1 file.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible. Current main stops the managed service before package replacement, and Windows Scheduled Task stop uses `/End` without disabling repeated triggers; I did not run a native Windows update in this read-only review.",
